products.title: Kaleidoscope Deluxe, Scarlet High Gloss - Venetian Blind

By combining a unique ribbon ladder with an immaculately polished surface that shimmers in the light we have created something a little special that will add a deluxe touch to any room in the home. Turn the living room into the colourful and relaxing space you have always wanted it to be by pairing scarlet with some cobalt blue walls and wooden flooring.
